{"tid":809432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★元朗IT人自殺亡！","createTime":"2018-09-07T07:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T07:47:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"98b0abbcb2e4a90ba764ae92252dc37ee8120b8f","tid":809432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"元朗大樹下東路崇山新村一間鐵皮屋，今早(7日)8時22分，一對男女拆下假天花，以繩索自縊身亡，女死者胞姐登門揭發報警，警方正展開調查，暫列屍體發現案處理。至早上10時許，探員抵現場蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，男死者27歲，是華裔挪威人，患有骨痛；女死者25歲，兩人為同居情侶關係。<span style=\"color: red;\">男事主從事IT工作</span>，與女友同在本港大專任職，本月5日，兩人最後露面。據悉，上址村屋門口貼有一張紙條，內容大致是「我們自殺了，不要進來，快報警。」警方相信是兩人留下的遺書，正調查兩人尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180907/bkn-20180907090431315-0907_00822_001.html?view=d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180907%2Fbkn-20180907090431315-0907_00822_001.html%3Fview%3Dd&d=OZDGa8eCb4G2idw2znjWXDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c02e4d01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180907/bkn-20180907090431315-0907_00822_001.html?view=d</a>"},{"pid":"0ce91c735b50ecd0d85c1218977e9facba3c363f","tid":809432,"uid":163024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"骨痛可能先係自殺嘅原因"},{"pid":"d385e3be49ca2081b0ca92bed640f37178646504","tid":809432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce91c735b50ecd0d85c1218977e9facba3c363f","tid":809432,"uid":163024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"骨痛可能先係自殺嘅原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"炒膿700？"},{"pid":"e09a522b32e3acb111b01d8b283dd0d975bc4331","tid":809432,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"華裔挪威人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo